1)  Create folder and Open in VS code

2)  Create Subfolder Config , Model , Controller . and create app.js

3)  Install Dependency Like express,nodemon,body-parser.
	npm init (Create Package.json)
	npm install -g nodemon
	npm install --save express
	npm install body-parser
	npm install --save mongoose
	
4) In Config folder create db.js file

5) In  Model folder create ___Model.js

6) In Controller folder create  ___Controller.js

7) import controller in app.js




